STATE v. McWHITE. No. COA06-18. North Carolina Court of Appeals. Filed December 5, 2006. Certification Date December 27, 2006. Appeal from Guilford (04CRS24257, 04CRS24263).

Case reported without published opinion. No error as to conviction for habitual misdemeanor assault and habitual felon status; vacated as to conviction for assault on a female; remanded for resentencing.
